data.description: Huge energy savings with brand new solar panels that drastically reduce your monthly electric bill! Calling all Veterans!!! This home's VA loan is assumable at a lower than low interest rate at 2.375%! No need to worry about the roof or the HVAC. They were both replaced in 2021. At first glance, you will notice the home's curb appeal from the long paver driveway, stone-faced siding, and the professionally curbed landscaping. This POOL home is in the highly desirable neighborhood of Town Park on a large lot with water fountain and sunset views. Step inside and take in the vaulted ceilings and open concept floor plan that seamlessly flows from the spacious living room, dining room, and updated kitchen with a breakfast nook. The kitchen is upgraded with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, soft closing cabinets and drawers with slide out shelves. Sliders welcome you out to the backyard oasis with a covered lanai, inground private pool complete with a screened pool enclosure.  There are 3 large bedrooms along with a spacious 14X13 bonus room, office, or 4th bedroom with tray ceilings and tile flooring. The primary bedroom retreat has tile flooring, tray ceilings, double vanities, jetted tub, his and her closets, a safe room, and a slider leading out to the lanai. Plantation shutters, inside laundry with a utility sink, and an air-conditioned oversized garage are some more bonuses that this home offers. This home is truly move in ready. This is the opportunity to call this YOUR home!
